{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01QHwAznPVLsHHysui4Ua5JT","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01W4bp1Cq2sJJoN9Qr6445ZC","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"- Story returned to `in-progress` for AC2 fix.","new_string":"- Story returned to `in-progress` for AC2 fix.\n\n### 8-9-semgrep-rules-rust-observability — dev-story fix cycle (2026-03-23T09:00Z)\n\n- **Semgrep not installed locally** — Cannot run `semgrep --validate` to confirm the rule parses correctly at the Semgrep engine level. The fix is structurally correct (match arms must be inside match blocks), but full validation requires semgrep-core.\n- No workarounds, no tech debt added. Single-file YAML fix."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":413,"cache_read_input_tokens":45920,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":413},"output_tokens":65,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6dce843f-9ba8-4a40-8e6f-55f9620fecc1","uuid":"d79f75e8-9124-49a0-92f7-70300550540d"}
