iner (Cargo.toml + src/main.rs with functions lacking tracing). Run codeharness audit and check that Rust rules are used.\n\n### For AC5:\nRun: docker exec codeharness-verify codeharness --version\n\n## Observability Check\nAfter key docker exec commands, query logs:\ncurl 'http://localhost:9428/select/logsql/query?query=_stream_id:*&start=-30s&limit=100'\n\n## Write Proof Document\nWrite to: verification/8-9-semgrep-rules-rust-observability-proof.md\n\nFormat each AC as:\n## AC N: <description>\n\\`\\`\\`bash\ndocker exec codeharness-verify <command>\n\\`\\`\\`\n\\`\\`\\`output\n<actual output>\n\\`\\`\\`\n\nIMPORTANT: Only use bash and output as code fence languages. Never use bare fences.\n\n## Rules\n1. ALL commands via docker exec codeharness-verify\n2. NO source code access\n3. Report REAL failures only\n4. [ESCALATE] only for genuinely impossible-to-automate things\" 2>&1","description":"Run black-box verifier (attempt 2)","timeout":300000},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":180,"cache_read_input_tokens":71916,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":180},"output_tokens":57,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6dce843f-9ba8-4a40-8e6f-55f9620fecc1","uuid":"3fe9f701-b7f5-4bd7-b1cf-ef193ed21c7f"}
